Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.75,0:02:18.09,S3-OP,,0,0,0,,給予味覺粗暴快感
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.09,0:02:20.46,S3-OP,,0,0,0,,Don't stop, don't stop, eating
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.46,0:02:23.30,S3-OP,,0,0,0,,Don't stop, don't stop, one more bite
